<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>내 위시리스트</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", system-ui, sans-serif;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .wish-container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h2 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; }

        .nav-links { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #64748b; }
        .nav-links a { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: #0ea5e9; text-decoration: underline; }

        .wish-item { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 18px 25px; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.01); }
        .wish-item-info { font-size: 16px; color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; }

        .btn-delete { background-color: #fff1f2; color: #f43f5e; border: 1px solid #fda4af; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-delete:hover { background-color: #f43f5e; color: white; }
        .btn-cart { background-color: #0f172a; color: white; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-cart:hover { background-color: #1e293b; }

        .empty-wish-box { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 16px; padding: 60px 40px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; }
        .empty-wish-box p { color: #64748b; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .btn-go-shopping { display: inline-block; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 35px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2); transition: 0.2s; }
        .btn-go-shopping:hover { background-color: #0284c7; transform: translateY(-1px); }

        .recommend-section { margin-top: 50px; }
        .recommend-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 2px solid #0f172a; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .shopping-item-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 20px; }
        .shopping-card-box { background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; flex-direction: column; transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s; }
        .shopping-card-box:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); }
        .card-img-wrapper { width: 100%; height: 160px; background-color: #f1f5f9; overflow: hidden; }
        .card-img-wrapper img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .card-info-content { padding: 15px; flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: left; }
        .card-info-content h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; margin: 0 0 6px 0; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .card-price-line { margin-top: auto; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wish-container">
    <h2>❤️ 내 위시리스트 목록</h2>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="products">商品 보러가기</a> | <a href="mypage">마이페이지</a>
    </div>
    <hr style="border: 0; height: 1px; background: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 25px;">

    <% if (wishlistItems.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="empty-wish-box">
            <p>위시리스트가 비어 있습니다. 마음에 드는 음료를 찜해보세요!</p>
            <a href="products" class="btn-go-shopping">음료 구경하러 가기</a>
        </div>

        <div class="recommend-section">
            <div class="recommend-title">🥤 이런 음료는 어떠세요?</div>
            <div class="shopping-item-grid">
                <% featuredProducts.forEach(product => { %>
                    <div class="shopping-card-box" onclick="location.href='products'" style="cursor:pointer;">
                        <div class="card-img-wrapper">
                            <img src="images/<%= product.image || 'default.png' %>" alt="<%= product.name %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-info-content">
                            <h4><%= product.name %></h4>
                            <div class="card-price-line">
                                ₩<%= product.price.toLocaleString() %>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>
    <% } else { %>
        <div class="wish-list">
            <% wishlistItems.forEach(item => { %>
                <div class="wish-item">
                    <span class="wish-item-info"><strong><%= item.name %></strong> - ₩<%= item.price.toLocaleString() %></span>
                    <div style="display: flex; gap: 6px;">
                        <form action="cart/add" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                            <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.id %>">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn-cart">담기</button>
                        </form>
                        <form action="wishlist/delete" method="POST" style="margin:0;">
                            <input type="hidden" name="productId" value="<%= item.id %>">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn-delete">제거</button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <% }) %>
        </div>
    <% } %>
</div>
</body>
</html>